claim.claim-text:
10. An optical element holder comprising:
a pedestal;
a holding section, located on the pedestal, for holding an optical element, the holding section including a pair of holding elements formed so as to hold the optical element by pinching it therebetween;
a fixing section, located around the pedestal, for being welded and fixed to a carrier; and
a stress-preventing section, located between the fixing section and the holding section, for preventing transmitting a welding stress to the holding section from the fixing section.
